MIFCSTASTAGO(mi)  ; ; LZF 10/25/04 ; ASTM protocol STAGO  -STA COMPACT : (Bi-Directional)
 	s mi=$g(mi) d
	S ^TMPMACH10(mi,104)=$H
	i '$l(mi) q
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)  //端口号
	//控制字符
  s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4)
  s lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),(result,epis)=""
	S ^TMPMACH10(mi,102)=$H

	i $$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  	c Port
  	q 
ErrHandler
	h 10
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q
Main 
  ;SET $ZTRAP="ErrHandler",$EC=""  
  r *R:10 e  d  q
  .d ORDER
  i $c(R)=enq d
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H<--M")
  .d ACK
  .f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  q:R=-1  d
  ..i $c(R)'=stx q
  ..s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,"",lf) q:'$l(record)
  ..s record=$e(record,1,$l(record)-1)
  ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$tr(record,$c(13,3)," "),"H<--M")
  .. ; check record validity
  ..d ACK
  .. ; query record
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["Q" d  q
  ...s epis=$p(record,"|",3)
  ...i $l(epis) s ^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ",epis)=""
  .. ; header record
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["H" d  q
  ...d Last s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""
  .. ; patient record
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["P" d  q
  ...s surname=$tr($tr($p(record,"|",6)," "),"^"," "),surname=$p(surname,cr,1)
  .. ; order record
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["O" d  q
  ...s epis=$tr($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",1)," ")  ;,QC=$tr($p(record,"|",12)," ") s:'$l(epis) epis=$tr($p($p(record,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
  ...s cup=$p($p(record,"|",4),"^",3)
  ...s episCur=""
  ...If +epis>190000,epis'="" Do
  ....If $length(epis)>5,$Data(^TEPI(epis)) Do
  .....Set episFlag=0
  .....Set TScode="" For  Set TScode=$Order(^TEPI(epis,1,TScode)) Quit:TScode=""  Do
  ......If $Length($Get(^TEPI(epis,1,TScode,1)))<20 Quit
  ......If mi1'=$piece($Get(^TEPI(epis,1,TScode,1)),"\",27) Quit
  ......Set episCur=$Piece($Get(^TEPI(epis,1,TScode,1)),"\",12)
  ...If episCur'="" Set epis=episCur
  .. ; result record
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["R" d  q
  ...s x1=$tr($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",4)," ")
  ...s x2=$tr($p(record,"|",4)," ") ; ,x3=$tr($p(record,"|",7)," ")
  ...i $l(x1),$l(x2) s result=result_x1_$c(92)_x2_$c(44)
  
  ..i $e(record,1,2)["M" d  q
  ...s (x1,x2)=""
  ...i $l(x1),$l(x2) s result=result_x1_$c(92)_x2_$c(44)
  ..I $e(record,1,2)["L" d Last q
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=eot:"EOT",1:R),"H<--M")
  .d ORDER
  q
Last  ; file result if exist
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
  i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
  s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""
  q
ORDER  ; create list of orders if exists
   i '$d(^TMP($zn)) q
   i '$d(^TMP($zn,$j)) q 
   k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   s labno="" f  s labno=$o(^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ",labno)) q:labno=""  d
   .//d SetTSMachine^MIF000(mi1,labno)  ;xulin 2009-11-2
   .d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)  ;^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",208912,"AH7471","A611071030",1)=
   .d PATDET(labno)
   .s tcx="",episx=epis
   .s chl="" f  s chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl)) q:chl=""  d
   ..s tcx="^^^"_chl
   .i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="O|1|"_labno_"||"_tcx_"|||||||||||Blood"
   .i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="L|1|F"

   .i '$l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="Q|1|^"_episx_"||^^^ALL||||||||X"
   .s ^DHCSTACOMPACT(+$h,$p($h,",",2),"M<-H",labno)=^TMIF(mi,22,line)
   k ^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ")
   q:'$d(^TMIF(mi,22))
   d Send k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   q
ERR
 s ^TMPMachErr(mi)=$ZERROR_".错误代码:"_$ECODE
 q 
   ///Batch Communication
BUILD   ; create list of orders if exists
   k ^TMIF(mi,22),^TMPstr
   s labno="" f  s labno=$o(^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,18,labno)) q:labno=""  d
   .s temepis=$p($p(^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,18,labno),"\",1),",",1)
   .s chlstr=$p(^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,18,labno),",",2)
   .d PATDET(labno)
   .s tcx="",episx=temepis
   .f temi=1:1:$l(chlstr,"\") d
   ..s chl=$p(chlstr,"\",temi)
   ..i '$l(chl) q
   ..s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"\"
   .i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="O|1|"_episx_"||"_tcx_"|R"
   .i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="L|1|N"
   .i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="H|\^&|||99^2.00|||||||P|1.00|"
   .i '$l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="Q|1|^"_episx_"||^^^ALL||||||||X"
   .m ^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,19,labno)=^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,18,labno)
   .k ^DHCMIFUPLOAD(mi,18,labno)
   q:'$d(^TMIF(mi,22))
   d Send k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   q
 
   ///RealTime Communication with epis
LoadList ; create list of orders if exists
   ///s labno="" f  s labno=$o(^DHCMIFLoadList(mi,"PEND",labno)) q:labno=""  d
   k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   //s labno="" f  s labno=$o(^DHCMIFLoadList(mi,"PEND",labno)) q:labno=""  d
   //.s temstr=^(labno)
   //.s chlstr=$p(temstr,"^",1)
   //.s temepis=$p(temstr,"^",2)
   //.d PATDET(labno)
   //.s tcx="",episx=temepis
   //.f temi=1:1:$l(chlstr,",") d
   //..s chl=$p(chlstr,",",temi)
   //..i '$l(chl) q
   //..s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"\"
   s labno="991784"
   d PATDET(labno)
   s tcx="^^^13"
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="O|1|"_labno_"||"_tcx_"|R"    
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="L|1|N"
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="H|\^&|||99^2.00|||||||P|1.00|"    
   i '$l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="Q|1|^"_labno_"||^^^ALL||||||||X"
   q:'$d(^TMIF(mi,22))
   d Send k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   q 
   
PATDET(epis)	; set patient details record
   s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="P|1|||^^^" 
   q
   
SET(epis,mode,rectemp)	; set record to be sent to instrument
   s tc="",tcx="",episx=epis
   i mode="SCAN" d
   .f k=3:1:$l(rectemp,"\")-1 d
   ..s tc=$TR($p(rectemp,"\",k),"F,P,I")
   ..s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_tc_"\"
   .s tcx=$e(tcx,1,$l(tcx)-1)                                 //O|1|00120025||^^^10\^^^11\^^^12|R
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="O|1|"_labno_"||"_tcx_"|R"
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="L|1|N"
   i $l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="H|\^&|||99^2.00|||||||P|1.00|"  ;"H|\^&|||99^2.10|||||||P|1.00|19990226103432"
   i '$l(tcx) s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,22,line)="Q|1|^"_episx_"||^^^ALL||||||||X"
   q
	     
Send  ; send list of orders if exists
   w enq,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H-->M")
   f j=1:1:10 r *R:1 i $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq) q
   d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"H<--M")
   i $c(R)=enq q
   i $c(R)'=ack w eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H-->M") q
   q:$$SEND("1H|\^&|||99^2.00|||||||P|1.00|")
   s sk="" 
   s sk=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,sk),-1)
   k ^TMIF(mi,22,sk) 
   s x="" f FRAME=2:1 s x=$o(^TMIF(mi,22,x)) q:x=""  q:$$SEND(FRAME#8_^TMIF(mi,22,x))
   w eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H-->M")
   k ^TMIF(mi,22)
   k ^TMIF(mi,10) 
   q
   
SEND(str)	; send string to instrument
   s ^tmpstago(+$h,$p($h,",",2),"H->M",1)=str
   s str=str_cr_etx,chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
   w stx,str,chsum,cr,lf,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str_chsum,"H-->M")
   f j=1:1:6 r *R:1 i ($c(R)=ack)!($c(R)=eot) q
   i $c(R)=ack d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H<--M") q 0
   i $c(R)=eot d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H<--M") q 0
   d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,R,"H<--M")
   q 1
   
CHSUM(x)	; calculate check sum
   n (x) s z=0 f y=1:1:$l(x) s z=z+$a(x,y)
   s z=$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#256\16+1)_$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#16+1)
   q z
   
ACK	    ; send 'ack' to instrument
   w ack,*-3
   d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H-->M")
   q
   
NEXTTRAY(tray)
   q tray

	q

医院名称

终端服务器地址 终端服务器端口号

仪器上接口标示和接口类型

  1. 接口类型：通过监听上传文件双向
  2. 连接方式：.hpr文件和.OK两个同目录不同文件

仪器接口说明

  • 仪器通过中间件共享到内网电脑，在内网电脑监听共享文件夹进行文件传输达成双向。一般在UpLoad文件读取文件，DownLoad上传双向文件
  • 通过旗标进行报警信息转换，生化项目较多，存储到结果说明造成his可以看到仪器的报警信息，因此本接口将报警信息保存到结果第三列其他结果处。
  • 对于BNP N端脑钠肽前体特殊处理，对于不同年龄不同结果有不同的解释，通过ConvertresKZJG方法进行转换，根据实际情况进行是否屏蔽。
  • 通过PreDeal.DealDemoM,PreDeal上传类，因此在M中可以写好文件名，文件内容后上传双向文件。输出本质是query，输出一条数据上传一个文件。

/// 获取扩展结果
ClassMethod ConvertresKZJG(mi, epis, code, res)
{
	s code=$g(code),res=$g(res)
	s OutPut=""

	s Labno=$$GetLabnoByEpis(mi,epis)
	i $l(Labno),$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Labno)) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Labno,""))
	.s Age=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR)),18)
	s Age=$g(Age)

	i '$l(code),'$l(res) q OutPut
	i code="BNP",0 d		// BNP N端脑钠肽前体
	.i '$l(Age) q
	.i Age<=50 d
	..i res<=450 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>450,res<=600 s OutPut="急性心衰"
	..i res>600 s OutPut="慢性心衰"
	.i ((Age>50)&&(Age<=75)) d
	..i res<=900 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>900 s OutPut="急性心衰"
	.i Age>75 d
	..i res<=1800 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>1800 s OutPut="急性心衰"

	i code="25OHD" d		// 25羟维生素D
	.i res<=20 s OutPut="缺乏"
	.i res>20,res<=30 s OutPut="不足"
	.i res>30,res<=100 s OutPut="充足"
	.i res>100 s OutPut="超上限"
	q OutPut

GetLabnoByEpis(mi,Epis)
	s ret=Epis,mi=$g(mi)
	s date=$zd($h,8)
	i '$l(mi) q Epis
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i '$l(WGMachineID) q Epis
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",date,WGMachineID,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Epis))) {
		s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",date,WGMachineID,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Epis),""),-1)
		S VisitNumberDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),2)
		s ret=$lg(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR),2)
		}
	q ret
}

	S $P(patRecord,"|",22)= diagnosis  	//诊断

	S PLIST($I(PLIST))=patRecord
	S order="O|1|"_labno_"||"_chlList_"|||||||||||||||||||||"

ClassMethod Other2Ten(snum, scale)
{
	s snum=$g(snum)
	s tnum=0
	s numlong=$l(snum)
	f i=1:1:$L(snum) d
	.s numi=$e(snum,i)
	.s numi=$$Sixteen(numi)
	.s tnum=tnum+(numi*(scale**(numlong-i)))
	q tnum
Sixteen(numi)
	i (numi="A")||(numi="a") s numi=10
	i (numi="B")||(numi="b") s numi=11
	i (numi="C")||(numi="c") s numi=12
	i (numi="D")||(numi="d") s numi=13
	i (numi="E")||(numi="e") s numi=14
	i (numi="F")||(numi="f") s numi=15
	q numi
}

/// w ##class(YHR.Problem.ScaleConversion).scaleconversion3()

	s snum=$g(snum)

	f i=1:1:10 q:(snum=0)||'$l(snum)  d
	.s pnum1=snum
	.s snum=$p(snum/scale,".",1)
	.s pnum2=pnum1#scale
	.s pnum2=$$Sixteen(pnum2)
	.s tnum=pnum2_tnum
	i scale=2 d
	.s tnum=..zeroize(tnum,8)
	q tnum

Sixteen(pnum2)

	i pnum2=13 s pnum2="D"

	q pnum2

{
	s ^TMP("zlz")=$lb(RowID, TestCodeDRS, TestCodePakDRS, FromInfo, MachineResDR, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions)

	s TestCodeDRS=$g(TestCodeDRS)

	s FromInfo=$g(FromInfo)

	s VisitNumberDR=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(VisitNumberReportDR)),2)

	s NewReportObj.VisitNumberReportDR=VisitNumberReportDR
	s NewReportObj.OrderNo=OrderNo
	s NewReportObj.Status="1"
	s sc=NewReportObj.%Save()
	i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d
	.THROW ##class(%Exception.SystemException).%New("事务委托","D",,"-1^保存失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc))
	s NodeName=""
	//默认结果关系
	s DefResultMap=""
	//按包取项目默认结果
	i $l(TestCodePakDRS) d
	.f i=1:1:$l(TestCodePakDRS,"^") d
	..s PakDR=$p(TestCodePakDRS,"^",i)
	..i '$l(PakDR) q
	..s NodeName=$lg($g(^dbo.BTIDPTestCodePakD(PakDR)),3)
	..//组装项目明细

	...s OneTestCodeDR="" f  s OneTestCodeDR=$o(^dbo.BTIDPTestCodePakItemI("IndexMaster",PakDR,TSSequence,OneTestCodeDR)) q:OneTestCodeDR=""  d
	....s ItemDR="" f  s ItemDR=$o(^dbo.BTIDPTestCodePakItemI("IndexMaster",PakDR,TSSequence,OneTestCodeDR,ItemDR)) q:ItemDR=""  d
	.....s DefResultMap(OneTestCodeDR)=$lg($g(^dbo.BTIDPTestCodePakItemD(ItemDR)),4)

	//插入项目

	i $l(TestCodeDRS) d
	.f i=1:1:$l(TestCodeDRS,"^") d
	..s TestCodeDR=$p(TestCodeDRS,"^",i)
	..i '$l(TestCodeDR) q
	..s ResultFormat=$lg($g(^dbo.BTTestCodeD(TestCodeDR)),9)
	..i '$l(NodeName) s NodeName=$lg($g(^dbo.BTTestCodeD(TestCodeDR)),3)
	..i $d(HasAddTestCode(TestCodeDR)) q
	..s ResultObj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberRepMidRes).%New()
	..s ResultObj.VisitNumberRepMidDR=NewReportObj.RowID
	..s ResultObj.TestCodeDR=TestCodeDR
	..//默认值

	..s DefResultTxt=$g(DefResultMap(TestCodeDR))
	..s ResultFormat=$lg($g(^dbo.BTTestCodeD(TestCodeDR)),9)
	..i $l(ResultFormat),(ResultFormat="S"),($ISVALIDNUM(DefResult)) s DefResultTxt = $lg($g(^dbo.BTTestCodeCommentsD(DefResult)),4)
	..i $l(ResultFormat),(ResultFormat="A"),($ISVALIDNUM(DefResult)) s DefResultTxt = $lg($g(^dbo.BTABOBGD(DefResult)),3)
    ..i $l(ResultFormat),(ResultFormat="R"),($ISVALIDNUM(DefResult)) s DefResultTxt = $lg($g(^dbo.BTRHBGD(DefResult)),3)
	..s ResultObj.Result=DefResult
	..s ResultObj.TextRes=DefResultTxt
	..i $l(MachineResDR) d
	...s ResultObj.Result=$lg($g(^dbo.RPMachineResultD(MachineResDR)),7)
	...s ResultObj.TextRes=$lg($g(^dbo.RPMachineResultD(MachineResDR)),8)
	..s ResultObj.OrderNo=i

	..s HasAddTestCode(TestCodeDR)=""
	..i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d
	...THROW ##class(%Exception.SystemException).%New("事务委托","D",,"-1^保存失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc))
	..i $l(MachineResDR) d
	...d ..CopyMachineAntRes(MachineResDR,ResultObj.RowID)

	//构造报告的鉴定过程节点
	s objNode=##Class(dbo.IDPResult).%New()
	s objNode.IDPElementDR=$lg($g(^dbo.IDPResultD(RowID)),3)
	s objNode.ActDate=$zd($h,8)
	s objNode.ActTime=$p($h,",",2)
	s objNode.ActUserDR=UserDR
	s objNode.AddDate=$zd($h,8)
	s objNode.AddTime=$p($h,",",2)
	s objNode.AddUserDR=UserDR
	s objNode.LinkRepMidDR=NewReportObj.RowID
	s objNode.Remark=NodeName
	s objNode.Sequence=OrderNo
	s objNode.ParentDR=RowID
	s objNode.VisitNumberReportDR=VisitNumberReportDR
	s objNode.MakeType="1"
	s objNode.FromInfo=FromInfo
	s sc=objNode.%Save()
	i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d
	.THROW ##class(%Exception.SystemException).%New("事务委托","D",,"-1^保存失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc))
	q objNode.RowID
}

ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record As %String(MAXLEN=99999999), epis, fileNameOrColName, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q
    s (sample,epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
    i '$l(record) q
    s record=$tr(record,"□"," ")
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,fileNameOrColName,"fileNameOrColName")
	s Deli="~" //结果分隔符
	s RDdli="," //通道号分隔符
	s ItemDeli=$c(92) //项目分隔符92
	s ResultDeli=$c(44) //结果分隔符44

	s (VisitNumber,Epis)=""

	s imgFlag=0
	s ret=""
	k ^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Data",mi)
	b ;a102
	//单项目
	for i=1:1:$l(record,"[13][10]") d
	.s rec=$p(record,"[13][10]",i)
	.i '$l(rec) q
	.;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,rec,"rec")
	.s type=$p($p(rec,"<",2)," ",1)
	.i (rec="<A>")||(rec="<B>")||(rec="<C>")||(rec="<D>")||(rec="<E>") d
	..s ^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Type")=$p($p(rec,"<",2),">",1)
	.i type="row" d rowInfo
	.i (rec="</A>")||(rec="</B>")||(rec="</C>")||(rec="</D>")||(rec="</E>") d
	..k ^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Type")
	.i rec="<F>" s imgFlag=1
	.i imgFlag=1 d imgInfo
	.i rec="</F>" s imgFlag=0

	i $l(VisitNumber) s epis=VisitNumber
	e  s epis=Epis
	i $l(epis) s epis=+epis

	i $d(^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Data",mi,"image")) d imgInfo
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ret,"image")
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
    i $l(epis),$l(result) d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
  
    k ^LISMachine("XDN9003C")
	q ret

rowInfo
	s Type=$g(^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Type"))
	s code=$p($p(rec,"name=",2),">",1)
	s code=Type_$tr(code,"""","")
	s res=$p($p(rec,">",2),"<",1)
	i code="A条形码",$l(res) s VisitNumber=res
	i code="B样本号",$l(res) d
	.s Epis=res
	.i $l(Epis)>6 d
	..s Epis=$e(res,7,*)
	i imgFlag=1 s ^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Data",mi,"image",code)=res
    s result=result_code_ItemDeli_res_ResultDeli
    q
  
imgInfo

	// ^LISMachine("Data",mi,"image")
	s imageClassStr=""
	s imagePath=""
	// D:\LISDATA\DATA\output.xml
	s imageRootPath=$replace(fileNameOrColName,$p(fileNameOrColName,"\",*),"")
	s code="" f  s code=$o(^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Data",mi,"image",code)) q:code=""  d
	.s res=$g(^LISMachine("XDN9003C","Data",mi,"image",code))
	.s imageClass=$p(res,".",1)
	.s imageClassStr=imageClassStr_imageClass_","
	.s res=imageRootPath_res
	.s imagePath=imagePath_res_","
    q:'$l(imageClassStr)
    s ret="getimage#"_epis_"#"_imageClassStr_"#"_imagePath
	q
}

				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"blockConnect")
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="GB18030"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"重新连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"reConnect")
				s LinkTime=0
				continue
				}
			//连接无数据传输，main每执行6次，即1min，重启tcp
			i $ZA="28674" s LinkTime=$i(LinkTime)
			//正常传输了，就清空计数
			i $ZA="28672" s LinkTime=0
			d Main
	 	}catch ex{
		 s exception="错误:"_ex.Location_"^"_ex.Data_ex.Name
		 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,exception,"读取或写入异常，重启服务端")
	 	}
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}

    Q

	i $$Start^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  	c Port
  	q
  	*/
  
ErrHandler
    h 10
    s iError=+$g(iError)+1
    i iError>100 s ret=$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)  q
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$tr($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    q
  
  
Main   
	SET $ZTRAP="ErrHandler" S iERR=0
	s Allrecord=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,SB,EB,"","",2) i '$l(Allrecord) q
	s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""

	for i=1:1:$l(Allrecord,cr) {
		s record=$p(Allrecord,cr,i)
		q:'$l(record)
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
		S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
		;消息段(数据类型) 	MSH	  MSA 	PID   OBR  	OBX  ORD  QRF 	ERR   QAK    DSP     DSC   
		I segmentType="MSH" {   //信息头信息
		    S mshStr=record
		    //消息类型
		    S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR 
		    I msgType="ORU" {
		        D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
		    }
		    I msgType="ORM" {
		    }
		    I msgType="QRY" {

		    }
		    S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
		}

		I segmentType="PID" {   //患者信息
		      
		}

		I segmentType="PVI" {   //就诊信息
		      
		}

		I segmentType="OBR" {   //医嘱信息
		    S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
		    S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(record,"|",4)
		    S dateStr=$P(record,"|",8)
		    I dateStr?14N {
		        S date=$ZDH($E(dateStr,1,4)_"-"_$E(dateStr,5,6)_"-"_$E(dateStr,7,8),3)

		    S channel=$P(record,"|",4)

		    S:'$L(sampleIdEnd) sampleIdEnd=sampleIdStart

		    I qryStartDate?1.N,qryEndDate?1.N {
